llm_results.raw_output:
import re

def slugify(text):
    text = text.lower()
    text = re.sub(r'\s+', '-', text)
    text = re.sub(r'[^a-z0-9\-]', '', text)
    text = re.sub(r'-+', '-', text)
    return text.strip('-')
